line_2: When the proud land its destin'd Conqueror own'd

line_1: Hark! universal nature shook and groan'd,
line_2: 'Twas the last trumpet — see the judge enthron'd:

line_1: Armies of Martyrs that in Exile groan'd,
line_2: States that their New Captivity bemoan'd,

line_1: And sympathizing Rocks in Eccho groan'd,
line_2: Can we forget how ev'ry Creature moan'd,

line_1: Give HOLLAND peace, whilst ENGLISH victims groan'd,
